        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on JHF’s book [<hi rend="italic">Souvenirs entomologiques</hi> (1879)].</p> 
            <p>Discusses story told by Erasmus Darwin about a wasp cutting off wings of fly.</p>
            <p>Sorry JHF is opposed to descent theory.</p>
            <p>Suggests experiment concerning insects’ sense of direction.</p>
        </abstract>
